description: Lists the history of the specified data lineage node.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the domain where you want to list the history of the specified data lineage node.

parameters.name: identifier
parameters.description: The ID of the data lineage node whose history you want to list.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When the number of history items is greater than the default value for the MaxResults parameter, or if you explicitly specify a value for MaxResults that is less than the number of items, the response includes a pagination token named NextToken. You can specify this NextToken value in a subsequent call to ListLineageNodeHistory to list the next set of items.

nested_items.name: nodes
nested_items.description: The nodes returned by the ListLineageNodeHistory action.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp at which the data lineage node was created.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The user who created the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: domainId
nested_items.description: The ID of the domain of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: eventTimestamp
nested_items.description: The event timestamp of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: sourceIdentifier
nested_items.description: The alternate ID of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: typeName
nested_items.description: The name of the type of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: typeRevision
nested_items.description: The type of the revision of the data lineage node.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp at which the data lineage node was updated.

nested_items.name: updatedBy
nested_items.description: The user who updated the data lineage node.
